Package: dataCleaning
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Cleaning Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nevil", "Maloba", email = "nevillemaloba@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to clean survey data, including reading Excel files,
    cleaning and shortening column names, converting categorical variables to factors,
    and saving the cleaned data in SPSS format with variable labels.
